Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}元の大きさに…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}-（魔女）ああっ…\N-（ニコ）ひっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:17:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（魔女）あが… 教える…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}ふう… いん…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}うが～ ああっ…
